const Detail = ({recipe}) => { return (

{recipe.name}

  • ID: {recipe.id}
  • Nombre: {recipe.name}
  • Resumen de plato: {recipe.summary}
  • Health Score: {recipe.healthScore}
  • Steps: {recipe.steps}
  • Img: {recipe.image}
  • Dietss: {recipe.diets.join(', ')}
); } export default Detail
